Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs42\pos(1205,50)}每天練習的飛鏢中了Double Bull
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs42\pos(1034,165)}4/22 07:05 [家中]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs42\pos(1117,204)}在用餐時看到電視中的殺人魔事件的報導
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs42\pos(1147,355)}似乎離自己家很近 而且犯人在逃走時 還路過了我就讀的中學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs42\pos(1104,283)}而且犯人在逃走時 還路過了我就讀的中學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs42\pos(1173,474)}4/22 07:45 [上學路上]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs42\pos(1250,526)}非常罕見地遇見了高阪和白石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常罕見地遇見了高阪和白石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高阪和白石為什麼偏偏今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是田徑部的吧 晨練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏在今天有這麼多巧合…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9點30分 學校2-B教室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有數學突擊考試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有寫答案哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是正確答案嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考得怎麼樣 雪輝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時一樣 比不過高阪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真掃興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12點32分 教室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休時又被高阪找碴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14點05分 料理實習室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡中切傷了手 去了保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個日記
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16點12分 回家路上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察在學校附近調查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有關電視上播出的殺人魔事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是可以知曉你未來的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明不是真實存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus 你是我幻想出來的神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是神 自然也能棲身於你的幻想之中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這個日記
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為知曉未來的代價 也有它的缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來日記就是所有者本身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來日記被破壞就等於你喪失了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 你會死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未來日記
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所見到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我接下來將要看見然後寫下的事情 已經被寫在了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告未來的無差別日記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝那傢伙 最近有點得意忘形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想教教他該怎麼做人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有點火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起埋伏他 挫挫他的銳氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 還不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14點12分 學校校舍後面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾個同學在埋伏我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是討厭我的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 只要不破壞未來就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿就是填滿答案的答卷一樣的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生贏家 我是超級人生贏家耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42\pos(626,408)}SIGN UP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.67,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42\pos(794,102)}小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.67,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42\pos(792,222)}考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火山老師 第3題搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓根沒學過這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我記得之前講過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼問題都小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可以預知未來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真靠不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不爽 就來試試讀取我的心聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不會那麼簡單就被你們看穿的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛剛瞄了一眼這邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我妻 現在可是在考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是讓大腦放鬆的體操
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要適可而止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績優秀 人也漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是整個學校嚮往的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:11:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dead End是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{an9\fs42\pos(419,438)}4/28 18:00 [放學路上]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,486)}好像有誰跟在我後面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(405,537)}4/28 18:21 [大樓內]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,585)}被殺人魔逼到絕境，被殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 那就是你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來又發生改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18時09分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在街上被我妻由乃攔截搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 會被她攔到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細思考 到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠做到這種事的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我以外應該沒別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我以外…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了嗎 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個日記所有者？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得飛鏢是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會讓你刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不會刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這種未來已經確定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你誤會了哦 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞上提到的殺人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三名日記所有者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是3rd
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3rd？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我預知到阿雪會被那傢伙殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過阿雪的未來之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的未來日記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18時20分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪會在大樓的14層死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面寫著的 全部都是我的事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的日記是雪輝日記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以10分為間隔 能夠掌握阿雪的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛的未來日記
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以10分鐘為間隔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:14:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止這傢伙一直每隔10分鐘就把我的事寫在日記上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個超級跟蹤狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說阿雪的未來是由乃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你干什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了 在14層下電梯的話會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 你就會成為生存遊戲的第一個出局者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存…遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來日記持有者互相窺伺著對方的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那傢伙一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在…說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪用日記用得太張揚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此在某處被他發現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這種地方幹什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他也持有未來日記嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論逃到哪裡都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 來到開闊的地方心情比較舒暢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這傢伙在一起的話 會死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡迎擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有辦法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛鏢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是決定你未來的飛鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的狀態怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙藏到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他使用未來日記的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「未來日記」在作為武器的同時 也是弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為日記相當於持有者本人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡… 他們逃到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 破壞他的「日記」的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 一起去吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽今天也不回家對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 Deus
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還有其他人持有未來日記
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得有說過日記持有者只有一人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣了 我一開始就說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的勝者 1st啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是傳聞中的1st嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你把那個殺人鬼給幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙是其他的日記所持者？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 既然所有人齊聚一堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就對這個「生存遊戲」進行說明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是你們持有的「日記」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個日記被稱為「未來日記」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來這個是你們平時用的普通日記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我扭曲了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使你們可以看到未來90天的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以稍微打斷一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾看到這個日記內容擅自變動了好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記所持者的行動會導致未來的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設持有者遇到了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被日記預告了將要受傷的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到持有者到達預告的時間點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而採取了不同於預告的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實就會發生變化 未來也會隨之改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能迴避預告中出現的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來要受傷的未來也會發生改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 未來的記述就被重寫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:19:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做 但日記也重寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記預告了我會被3rd殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能改變未來的並不一定只有你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什麼被稱為生存遊戲的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當日記持有者確定被會別的持有者殺死的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會出現死之宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Dead End的預告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你說了要殘殺 但我們也不知道相互的樣貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就需要你們使用自己日記裡的情報 然後找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說遊戲從追尋對方的真實身份開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是暴露了就會被殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出對方的真實身份 就能立起Dead End Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一遇到被他人立起Dead End Flag的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就需要拼盡全力進行迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是這場生存遊戲的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st 你本該在那個時候死去才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你卻反殺了對手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是超越奇跡的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能殺掉所有人最後贏得勝利的或許就是1st啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我最看好的人是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引發這個奇跡的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 在這場生存遊戲中取勝 最後留下人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就作為我的繼任者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把支配時間和空間的神之座讓出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生還是死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下11人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被殺死之前殺掉對手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只需贏取神之座就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來的話 首當其衝的障礙就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望別在我前去殺你之前就掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 加油哦 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我「看見」你在害怕了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠贏取奇跡的這份頑強 可是有點棘手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不對 不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:22:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就此閉會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個狀況是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.39,0:22:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪…由由乃來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆魯姆魯老師的裡未來日記 3rd的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綜上所述 3rd啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:24:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也被選為12個未來日記持有者之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目擊者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.85,0:24:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能讓她活著回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.97,0:24:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.33,0:24:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能稍微聽一下別人的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.55,0:24:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生存遊戲開始前就被消滅了 你到底想怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.98,0:24:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你寫下的殺人記錄 是殺人日記
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.41,0:24:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我借用一下 稍微設定了點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.02,0:24:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會拿著這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.11,0:24:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 吃驚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.81,0:24:40.62,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人的證據要毀滅…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.01,0:24:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可是能夠預知未來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.81,0:24:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說聽我說話啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.12,0:24:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.81,0:24:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑心病重的人真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.01,0:25:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總覺得無論怎樣的因果 第一個出局是3rd的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.90,0:25:17.95,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3800,0)\fs80\pos(649,501)}契 約 條 件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:35.57,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心が死ぬよ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:40.99,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自分の躊躇いがひきがねになるよ?????
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:43.58,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助けて君へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.17,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じて君からもれた声に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:53.67,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡を祈ろうか　だけど??　???
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:57.47,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲劇は終わらない鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:02.39,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇の奥で繰り返す叫び
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:09.31,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛みがり悪意　選ばれしBlood teller
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:13.57,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣きたくない　これ以上会いたくない?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.86,0:23:17.49,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃える　愛しさが交叉した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:21.66,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会いに来て　泣きたくて追いかけて??
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.99,0:23:25.87,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰にも止められない??
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:30.34,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これは未来　それとも夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:33.80,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答えはどこだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:38.39,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが今を試す扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:41.81,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊すのが開けなら?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:44.85,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:35.59,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任心死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:40.99,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自身的躊躇成為一切的誘因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:43.58,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你呼喊著求救
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.17,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「相信我」你發出的聲音搖曳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:53.69,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要祈求奇跡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:57.48,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是悲劇是永遠不會停歇的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:02.39,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗之中不停嘶吼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:09.32,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕痛楚的惡意 被選擇的Blood teller
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:13.57,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想哭泣 亦不想再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:17.49,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火光燃燒 憐愛相交
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:21.66,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來見我吧 強忍淚水一路追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:25.87,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何人可以阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:30.34,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是未來 還是夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.54,0:23:33.80,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案究竟位於何處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:38.39,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是試煉今朝的門扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:41.81,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果破壞即為開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:44.85,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又該如何選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:04.67,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs38}コンセンテス·デイ ユーノー ユーピテル ミネルウァ アポロ マールス ケレース
